                            <comment id="12894786" author="streamy" created="Tue, 3 Aug 2010 02:15:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After the master rewrite gets merged in it will be possible to retain assignment information in META during a shutdown and to then use it on the startup for the initial region assignment.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
